						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,504410)">Possible problem?</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/runner724" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(336859); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=336859&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610246704" alt="runner724" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=336859)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/runner724" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(336859); return false;" >runner724</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1244572092 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">09 Jun 2009 18:28</span>
		</div>
