			<div class="content" id="post-content-1590057">
									

<p>This is my favorite description of what is basically genesis. I like the logic of it but it gives the perfect amount of mystery as well as being one of the more well written articles I've ever read (which numbers in the thousands). I deleted my vote and re-voted a +1 just to make a point. But a theory comes to mind. If this is a potential way that SCP's are created, and it's under lock and key with ridiculous securities measures&#8230; How do they keep coming?</p>

